name: Cooking Clash
summary: Step into the chaos of Cooking Clash, the ultimate fast-paced restaurant game! As both the head chef and owner, you’ll be whipping up creative dishes for a lively mix of human and animal customers. Experiment with endless ingredient combinations to craft unique meals that keep diners coming back for more. But watch out—some sneaky guests have their eyes on your hard-earned tips! Can you keep the crowd happy while making sure your profits don’t disappear?
